abc64778-983e-48fc-a69c-303a25b396cd.title: King Bolren
abc64778-983e-48fc-a69c-303a25b396cd.text:
Well hello stranger. My name's Bolren, I'm the king of
the tree gnomes.

03220f50-bc0f-49f6-9f8f-23cb20d4ceee.title: King Bolren
03220f50-bc0f-49f6-9f8f-23cb20d4ceee.text:
I'm surprised you made it in, maybe I made the maze
too easy.

e7d0c8a2-a6ad-466f-acd5-eda1e5a2803c.title: King Bolren
e7d0c8a2-a6ad-466f-acd5-eda1e5a2803c.text:
I'm afraid I have more serious concerns at the
moment. Very serious.

options.text: I'll leave you to it then.

4e0a56c2-2cba-4baf-adb4-44bfa714f94c.title: <player>
4e0a56c2-2cba-4baf-adb4-44bfa714f94c.text: I'll leave you to it then.

59a337d8-e833-4304-8196-103da6e360d5.title: King Bolren
59a337d8-e833-4304-8196-103da6e360d5.text:
The truth is my people are in grave danger. We have
always been protected by the Spirit Tree. No creature
of dark can harm us while its three orbs are in place.

176d0e24-1e2b-4d35-8c16-575588a155b5.title: King Bolren
176d0e24-1e2b-4d35-8c16-575588a155b5.text:
We are not a violent race, but we fight when we must.
Many gnomes have fallen battling the dark forces of
Khazard to the North.

0d04f130-7b80-441b-b0d7-88daec887070.title: King Bolren
0d04f130-7b80-441b-b0d7-88daec887070.text:
We became desperate, so we took one orb of protection
to the battlefield. It was a foolish move.

c4ce9646-8a9a-448f-af6b-418f6e29529c.title: King Bolren
c4ce9646-8a9a-448f-af6b-418f6e29529c.text:
Khazard troops seized the orb. Now we are completely
defenceless.

7b250295-b178-456d-a14d-c6e63c5a8be7.title: King Bolren
7b250295-b178-456d-a14d-c6e63c5a8be7.text:
You would be a huge benefit on the battlefield. If you
would go there and try to retrieve the orb, my people
and I will be forever grateful.

a7e7033b-f46f-4720-8298-ac68b8dadf6d.title: <player>
a7e7033b-f46f-4720-8298-ac68b8dadf6d.text: I'm sorry but I won't be involved.
